<%- include("background.ejs") %>

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
    }

    .barkot-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(47, 69, 7, 0.7), rgba(47, 69, 7, 0.7)), url('https://placehold.co/1500x500/9A8B7A/9A8B7A') no-repeat center center/cover;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .barkot-hero h1 {
        font-size: 3.5em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .barkot-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 40px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .location-section {
        margin-bottom: 50px;
        padding-bottom: 30px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    
    .location-section:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .location-section h2 {
        color: #2f4507;
        font-size: 2.5em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border-left: 5px solid #2f4507;
        padding-left: 15px;
    }

    .location-section p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .highlight-box {
        background-color: #e8f5e9;
        border-left: 5px solid #d32f2f;
        padding: 25px;
        margin: 20px 0 30px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .highlight-box p {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        color: #2f4507;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
     .highlight-box span {
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .aid-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .aid-list li {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .aid-list li::before {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        margin-right: 15px;
    }

    /* Unique icons */
    .aid-list .hygiene::before { content: 'üßº'; }
    .aid-list .shelter::before { content: '‚õ∫'; }
    .aid-list .utensils::before { content: 'üç¥'; }
    .aid-list .bedsheets::before { content: 'üõèÔ∏è'; }
    .aid-list .blankets::before { content: 'üß£'; }
    .aid-list .lights::before { content: 'üí°'; }
    .aid-list .ration::before { content: 'üçö'; }


    .gallery-section h3 {
        color: #2f4507;
        font-size: 2.2em;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .gallery-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .gallery-item img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .gallery-item img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    
    .call-to-action {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 50px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
    }

    .call-to-action p {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
</style>

<div class="barkot-hero">
    <h1>Responding to Disasters Across Uttarakhand</h1>
</div>

<div class="barkot-container">

    <div class="location-section">
        <h2>On the Frontlines of Hope near Syanachatti</h2>
        <p>Two months ago, torrential rains and landslides struck Uttarkashi near Syanachatti, washing away the vital bridge that connected villages like Kunsala, Kupra, and Trikhli. Overnight, hundreds of families were left cut off from the outside world. Schools shut down, crops were delayed, and access to medical care became nearly impossible.</p>
        
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p>At such a critical moment, <span>Mountain Forum Himalayas</span> stepped in, reaching these three cut-off villages and providing relief support to <span>200 affected families.</span></p>
        </div>

        <ul class="aid-list">
            <li class="ration">Ration Kits</li>
            <li class="shelter">Shelter Kits</li>
            <li class="hygiene">WASH Kits</li>
            <li class="blankets">Blankets</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="gallery-section">
            <h3>Glimpses from the Syanachatti Area</h3>
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="bar1.jpg" alt="Relief Efforts 1">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="bar2.jpg" alt="Relief Efforts 2">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="bar3.jpg" alt="Relief Efforts 3">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="location-section">
        <h2>Critical Support in Kupra Village</h2>
        <p>Mountain Forum Himalayas also delivered essential, focused relief to 140 disaster-affected families specifically in Kupra village, near Barkot, to ensure they had the necessary supplies to rebuild and maintain their health and safety.</p>

         <ul class="aid-list">
            <li class="hygiene">Hygiene Kits</li>
            <li class="shelter">Shelter Kits</li>
            <li class="utensils">Utensils</li>
            <li class="bedsheets">Bedsheets</li>
            <li class="blankets">Blankets</li>
            <li class="lights">Solar Lights</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="gallery-section">
            <h3>Glimpses from Kupra Village</h3>
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="kupra1.jpg" alt="Kupra Relief 1">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="kupra2.jpg" alt="Kupra Relief 2">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="kupra3.jpg" alt="Kupra Relief 3">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="call-to-action">
        <p>This is more than just an emergency response. It is a pledge to stand shoulder to shoulder with the most vulnerable mountain communities, ensuring they are not forgotten in times of crisis.</p>
    </div>

</div>

